Explain each of the following:

ng-app:
ng-controller:
$scope: Manages the action between controller and view "glue"
ng-model: "data Binding"
{{}}: "binding" "data Binding"
ng-repeat: Iterate or repeat multiple times.
filters: Filters out only what you want.
Services/Factory:
Directives: how to do fancy things with the view.
ng-show (Not in Video): Helps with showing stuff
ng-click: deals with clicking stuff.